body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello! Thank you for contacting Car Dealership Support. My name is Jordan Hayes.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: May I have your name please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hi Jordan! My name is Victoria Gonzales.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Victoria. To better assist you, could you provide me with your contact number, spelling out the digits?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Of course, it's six three zero, five five five, eight eight one one.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Victoria. Could you also confirm your address for verification purposes?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Yes, it's two one zero, Elm Street, Cityville, State.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for the information, Victoria. We will look into the billing issue related to your recent visit.

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I appreciate it, Jordan. I was feeling disappointed about the billing error.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I understand, Victoria. Your concern will be resolved promptly. Thank you for your time.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Have a great day, Victoria! Goodbye.
